        " رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : «إِذَا طَرَقَكُمْ سَائِلٌ ذَكَرٌ بِلَيْلٍ فَلاَ تَرُدُّوهُ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1737 - The Messenger of Allah (swt), peace and blessings be upon him and his family, said:\n\"If a male beggar comes to you at night, do not turn him away.\""
        ]
